# Math Battle :game_die:

Math Battle is a fun web-based game where you can solve basic math problems and challenge your friends to see who can solve them the fastest. :rocket:

## Features :sparkles:

- Solve addition (+), subtraction (-), multiplication (x), and division (รท) problems.
- Play against the computer or invite your friends for a multiplayer challenge. :busts_in_silhouette:
- Track your score and compete for high scores. :trophy:
- Choose from different difficulty levels to suit your skills. :star:

## Demo :computer:

You can try out the live demo of Math Battle [here](https://mathbattletg.netlify.app/). :link:

## Getting Started :rocket:

To run Math Battle locally on your machine, follow these steps:

1. Clone the repository: `git clone https://github.com/TheOrangehat/math-battle.git`
2. Navigate to the project directory: `cd math-battle`
3. Open `index.html` in your preferred web browser.

## Contributing :handshake:

We welcome contributions from the community to improve Math Battle. If you would like to contribute, please follow these steps:

1. Fork the repository.
2. Create a new branch: `git checkout -b feature/your-feature`
3. Make your changes and commit them: `git commit -m 'Add your feature'`
4. Push the changes to your fork: `git push origin feature/your-feature`
5. Open a pull request on the main repository.

## Feedback and Support :speech_balloon:

If you have any questions, suggestions, or need assistance with Math Battle, please [open an issue](https://github.com/your-username/math-battle/issues) on the GitHub repository. :raised_hands:

